iFat	
iApril 07th, 2018	
i----------------------------------------	
i	
iI keep track of my weight and a bunch of other measurements with	
ia little shell function that logs to a csv file on dropbox. A year	
iago I made some fantastic progress but then it all fell apart.	
iWith the new year I started getting back into my good habits and	
ionce again was making progress. Last month I got really sick: flu,	
ipneumonia, blah blah. I fell off the wagon (a food wagon) and have	
ibeen eating like crap once again.	
i	
iTomorrow it's back on diet again (keto) and I know I'll feel so	
imuch better soon. To help prep me mentally I decided to plot my	
iweight progress.	
i	
